23			Long: `Manage beads — portable, ephemeral work items with metadata.
24	
25	Beads provide a lightweight work queue for AI agents and developers.
26	They track tasks, dependencies, and status without coupling to any
27	specific workflow methodology.
28	
29	Examples:
